select 
    min (mta_tax) id,
    max(total_amount) total_amount ,
    avg(id) id_avg,
    count(distinct surcharge) surcharge
from dbo.FaresData_Fast
group by [payment_type]

select 
    min (mta_tax) id,
    max(total_amount) total_amount ,
    avg(id) id_avg,
    count(distinct surcharge) surcharge
from dbo.FaresData_Slow
group by [payment_type]
